holes.original_proof:
intro n hn
induction' hn with n hn IH
norm_num [Nat.factorial_succ, Nat.pow_succ]
cases n with
| zero => contradiction
| succ n =>
  cases n with
  | zero => contradiction
  | succ n =>
    cases n with
    | zero => contradiction
    | succ n =>
      cases n with
      | zero => contradiction
      | succ n =>
        cases n with
        | zero => contradiction
        | succ n =>
          cases n with
          | zero => contradiction
          | succ n =>
            cases n with
            | zero => contradiction
            | succ n =>
              cases n with
              | zero => contradiction
              | succ n =>
                cases n with
                | zero => contradiction
                | succ n =>
                  cases n with
                  | zero => contradiction
                  | succ n =>
                    cases n with
                    | zero => contradiction
                    | succ n =>
                      cases n with
                      | zero => contradiction
                      | succ n => simp_all [Nat.factorial_succ, Nat.pow_succ, Nat.mul_assoc] <;> nlinarith
